        "text": "You are a data extraction assistant. Analyze this French quote/offer document (PDF) and extract these fields.\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object with no explanation, no markdown, no code blocks.\n\nFields to extract:\n- file_id: Google File ID\n- dev_id: quote or offer number\n- date_ajout: document date (DD/MM/YYYY) no matter if the date is in the past\n- date_validite: validity end date (DD/MM/YYYY) no matter if the date is in the past\n- fournisseur: supplier company name\n- client: client company name\n- ref_client: client reference\n- contact: contact person name\n- vat: VAT number\n- produit: first product or service description\n- decription: second line of product or service description\n- qte_devis: quantity (number)\n- prix_unit: unit price (number)\n- total_devis: line total (number)\n\nIf a field is not found, set it to null.",
